      h1 ~Kuba Fietkiewicz/
      h4 Engineer * Father * Leader
      p You can navigate by scrolling down, clicking on the buttons to the right, or entering commands below.

  section#contact
    h1 ~/Contact

  section#resume
    h1 ~/Resume

  section#work
    h1 ~/Work
    ul
      li http://calls.yp.com
      li stuff

  .command-console
